## 6. Fonts

The MashupForge brand typography ("AETHER SANS" and "NEXUS MONO")
is implemented in code via Google Fonts:

- **Space Grotesk** (mapped to "AETHER SANS") — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Space+Grotesk
- **JetBrains Mono** (mapped to "NEXUS MONO") — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono

Both fonts are loaded via `next/font/google`, which downloads them
at build time and self-hosts the WOFF2 files alongside the bundle.
No runtime call to fonts.googleapis.com is made.

